short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en_GB,en_US,e: Quickly export ,extract and backup your WhatsApp contacts by various dimensions such as Contacts, Chats, Groups, Labels, and…
short.en,en_AU: Export ,extract and backup your WhatsApp contacts by various dimensions such as Contacts, Chats, Groups, Labels, and Countries.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en_GB,en_US,e:
This powerful and user-friendly tool lets you extract and export all your WhatsApp contacts, including unknown phone numbers, with just a few clicks. With this extension, you can keep your data secure and choose from popular formats like CSV, Excel, JSON, or VCard to export your contacts.

Our tool is perfect for anyone who needs to backup and manage their WhatsApp contacts. Whether you need to export contacts for future use, organize your chat history, or backup your contacts in case of data loss or device transfer, our Export WhatsApp Contacts provides a simple and efficient solution.

Features:
✅ Easily extract and export all your WA contacts with just a few clicks
✅ Extract contacts from groups and chats to organize your contacts
✅ Filter contacts by country for targeted outreach or analysis
✅ Save contacts from labeled chats for easy reference and management
✅ Export data to popular formats like XLS, CSV, JSON, or VCard for secure backup and use in other applications.

Why use our Export WhatsApp Contacts?
✅ Save time: Quickly extract and export all your WA contacts with just a few clicks.
✅ Keep data secure: Choose from multiple export formats to ensure your data remains safe and confidential.
✅ Get organized: Categorize your contacts by groups, chats, labels, countries, and more for complete control over your data.
✅ Never lose contacts again: Easily backup and export your WA contacts for quick access when you need it.

Please note that our Export WA Contacts does not collect any personal data or violate any terms of service. It only extracts and exports WA contacts that are already stored on your device.

# Home Page
https://export-wa-contacts.wabulk.net/
